reviews.review_msg: This was a very different experience, as we did most of the work on-line. I felt a little uneasy about how we would be graded, as it was not really clear. In the end, I think we all got A's though, so I was happy! I just wish I knew not to worry about it!
Excellent prof! She could hand out the graded assignments sooner and participate in online discussions more often. Overall, she is worth checking out!
